Which--I think this is a quiz
question here,

00:28:02.097 --> 00:28:03.670
probably number five.
 

00:28:03.670 --> 00:28:04.598
Which is this?
 

00:28:04.598 --> 00:28:11.690
A major chord or a minor chord
&gt;

00:28:11.690 --> 00:28:12.589
as opposed to?
 

00:28:12.589 --> 00:28:17.910
