Okay. There's no beat to it.
 

00:32:36.460 --> 00:32:37.338
All right.
 

00:32:37.338 --> 00:32:40.490
It's very languid in terms of
the pulse here.

00:32:40.490 --> 00:32:44.259
It's very understated in terms
of a beat.

00:32:44.259 --> 00:32:48.787
You'd be hard pressed to
identify what the meter of that

00:32:48.787 --> 00:32:53.029
is so that's one reason,
and of course what--where am I

00:32:53.029 --> 00:32:57.067
going with the next important
point about what's happening in

00:32:57.067 --> 00:32:58.009
this music?
 

00:32:58.009 --> 00:33:06.477
It makes us feel serene,
relaxed, because it's all going

00:33:06.477 --> 00:33:12.019
down &lt;&lt;music
playing&gt;&gt;

00:33:12.019 --> 00:33:21.450
and only when we get here
&gt;

00:33:21.450 --> 00:33:24.720
