00:33:24.720 --> 00:33:29.037
So again, direction in music
also is important with how we

00:33:29.037 --> 00:33:30.250
respond to it.
 

00:33:30.250 --> 00:33:31.789
So what are we going over here?
 

00:33:31.789 --> 00:33:32.829
Major versus minor?
 

00:33:32.829 --> 00:33:35.980
Disjunct versus conjunct?
 

00:33:35.980 --> 00:33:36.890
What else?
 

00:33:36.890 --> 00:33:41.058
Strongly felt tonal key,
which is called--

00:33:41.058 --> 00:33:42.730
I don't know if I mentioned
