00:33:42.730 --> 00:33:44.692
the tonic key,
the tonic pitch,

00:33:44.692 --> 00:33:48.367
the tonic pitch there,
and this idea of the direction

00:33:48.367 --> 00:33:49.318
of the music.
 

00:33:49.318 --> 00:33:53.887
All of these we'll have to be
thinking about as we listen to

00:33:53.887 --> 00:33:55.670
music in this course.
 

