up.

00:48:10.360 --> 00:48:14.539
Raising up music builds
excitement.

00:48:14.539 --> 00:48:33.909
&gt;
 

00:48:33.909 --> 00:48:36.500
Now he builds--I think this is
the last question.

00:48:36.500 --> 00:48:38.929
What do we call this last chord?
 

00:48:38.929 --> 00:48:40.628
What &lt;&lt;music
playing&gt;&gt;

